T1  - Resolving the scale efficiency puzzle in banking
AU  - McAllister, Patrick H.
AU  - McManus, Douglas
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 17
IS  - 2
SP  - 389
EP  - 405
PY  - 1993
DA  - 1993/04/01/
